880
00:41:09,366 --> 00:41:10,534
‐ Yes.

881
00:41:10,659 --> 00:41:12,536
‐ There's a pattern here.
‐ Yes!

882
00:41:12,661 --> 00:41:14,955
‐ His car dealership
got busted, too.

883
00:41:15,039 --> 00:41:17,249
‐ Wait, sorry.
